<br><span style="display:none"> (<span class="bday">1947-07-05</span>) </span>July 5, 1947<span class="noprint ForceAgeToShow"> (age 77)</span><sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>2<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><br><div style="display:inline" class="birthplace">
